About this item
HIGH QUALITY: This glass pitcher is made of lead-free borosilicate material, which is healthy, non-toxic and safe to use. With food grade 304 stainless steel cover, dual water outlet design: large water outlet, smooth water flow / filter port: easy to filter ice cubes, fruits, tea bags, etc.
LARGE CAPACITY: The body of the pitcher has a precise scale on it. Maximum capacity is 2000ml/68oz,Fully capable of meeting daily needs，so you can prepare homemade drinks, iced tea, juices and more as needed. It’s suitable for family, restaurant, cafe shop, tea house.
COMFORTABLE AND CONVENIENT DESIGN: The anti-drip spout allows you to pour water smoothly during use without leaking. A larger handle and a snug-fitting lid make it easier to grab a jug and pour a drink. Particular Coaster can effectively provide anti slip and protection, and disassembly is simple.
EASY TO CLEAN: Glass water pitcher tanks with smooth surfaces are less likely to absorb dirt than other materials, so it’s easy to wash them clean with warm water. Wide mouth glass jugs are easier to clean, pitchers are safe to wash in the dishwasher.
